A11: ( 0 ) < x
and
A12: y < ( 0 );
( sgn x ) = 1 by A11,CKB15:def 1;
then A13: ( ( ( sgn x ) + ( sgn y ) ) + 1 ) = ( ( 1 + ( - 1 ) ) + 1 ) by A12,CKB15:def 1
.= 1;
((( x + y ) < ( 0 ) or ( x + y ) = ( 0 )) or ( 0 ) < ( x + y ));
hence thesis by A13,CKB15:def 1;
end;
A14: ((x < ( 0 ) & y < ( 0 )) implies ( sgn ( x + y ) ) <= ( ( ( sgn x ) + ( sgn y ) ) + 1 ))
